show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/ZkUayk
show.description: In a crumbling mental asylum, a woman dies in front of her young daughter, leaving behind a box of letters that uncover a haunting tale of betrayal, stolen identity, and a love torn apart. Years later, the estranged husband uncovers the shocking truth — the child he raised is not his own, but part of a cruel plan by a woman with dark intentions. Just when all hope seems lost, a mysterious twin appears, carrying the truth and a burning need for justice.
